<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> DeAngelis et al., Receptive-field dynamics in the central visual pathways, Trends Neurosci. 1995, <a href="/wiki/Entrez" title="Entrez">Entrez Pubmed</a> <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=pubmed&amp;dopt=Abstract&amp;list_uids=8545912" class="external text" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=pubmed&amp;dopt=Abstract&amp;list_uids=8545912" rel="nofollow">8545912</a></li>
